  "title": "Logistics Executive/ Warehouse Executive #80445",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Wholesale of Food Service Product</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Logistics Executive/ Warehouse Executive</strong></li><li>Working Location: Penjuru Lane</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Monday-Friday, 8.30am – 5.30pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + PB</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Support the warehouse manager in coordinating and overseeing day-to-day warehouse operations.</li><li>Resolve issues related to transportation logistics, logistics systems, import or export activities, and customer matters.</li><li>Lead the team to achieve departmental KPIs.</li><li>Lead and manage warehouse staff, including training and performance evaluations.</li><li>Control warehouse costs for OT, packing materials, stationery, pallets, and other items.</li><li>Monitor stock levels and maintain accurate inventory records.</li><li>Ensure all warehouse equipment operates smoothly and safely.</li><li>Maintain workplace safety and comply with all WSH requirements.</li><li>Receive and handle payments from customers and drivers.</li><li>Prepare the monthly warehouse report.</li><li>Communicate effectively to liaise with cross-functional teams.</li><li>Perform other ad-hoc duties as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or equivalent in Warehousing or a related field.</li><li>Strong analytical and problem-solving skills.</li><li>Experience in warehousing management.</li><li>Able to work independently and as part of a team.</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office applications, including Excel and Outlook.</li><li>Good interpersonal skills to communicate well with cross-functional stakeholders.</li><li>Customer oriented toward both internal and external customers.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#80445 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
